title: Mormon Tabernacle Choir Easter Concert - Handel's Messiah Apr 18
description:
This is the Mormon Tabernacle Choir's live performance of Handel's Messiah performed at the Salt Lake City Tabernacle on April 18 2014. This was broadcast live over the internet and available for viewing until April 21 11:59 PM MT. After that it will no longer be available to watch as they are in the process of making a studio recording of it. 

Enjoy and please seed.
